                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Sherman</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Draper</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1898-04-05">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 5, 1898</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Secretary of the Treasury has suspended the order relative to Ellis Island. Hope
                    to advise if further action during day.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Sherman.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
